        <abstract> 
<p>Response to [vol. 1 of] CD’s <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Not yet convinced on sexual selection and protection, though their differences are not so great as CD thinks.</p> 
<p>On man, he does not think CD has accounted for <hi rend="italic">every</hi> step of his development by "ascertained laws".</p> 
